Key Match Events: Jamal Musiala scored once and set up three more goals as Germany crushed Hungary 5-0.
Niclas Füllkrug scored the opening goal in the 27th minute.
Jamal Musiala scored in the 58th minute.
Florian Wirtz scored in the 66th minute.
Aleksandar Pavlovic scored in the 77th minute.
Kai Havertz scored in the 81st minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at the Merkur Spiel-Arena in Düsseldorf, Germany, in front of 49,235 spectators.
Germany won their first match of the Nations League competition with a 5-0 victory over Hungary.
